:"2019-07-16T18:31:21.000Z","msg":"諗住入嚟屌撚爆你個柒頭<br />\n點知樓豬原來開反話post<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"006eafbd69a5f2986938f9c5d12946518d1e9428","tid":1325032,"uid":270456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:32:21.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e18d520eab27fcf7f2387d55d6fd535aaf0df02","tid":1325032,"uid":83198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:33:30.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">721要上街！五大訴求，缺一不可！\n\n一、徹底撤回修例\n二、收回暴動定性\n三、釋放所有義士\n四、追究警隊濫權\n五、立即雙真普選\n\n不分化，不篤灰，不割蓆</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n唔喺金鐘玩game 可行嗎？"},{"pid":"209f2b46b283b938a87f9f341b7938edc8b9788a","tid":1325032,"uid":273297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:33:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>721見</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aacb3aeaaa35b4449a861e8c5884d52fa3abcd55","tid":1325032,"uid":197852,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"36f7f363120add964a4260dc09548b35c7778744","tid":1325032,"uid":109943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T17:45:19.000Z","msg":"屌 我一定出呀<br />\n唔好意思 唔好負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想你地記住721 一定要好好保護自己<br />\n包頭 頭盔 口罩 保護埋自己人<br />\n我地博盡！<br />\n<br />\n到時見"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:34:32.000Z","msg":"用下你個柒腦先開post好唔好<br />\n好多人睇到個咁既標題見到正皮多<br />\n真係以為721無人出嫁<br />\n屌你老母臭化系"},{"pid":"349b4512a4a146eb90f0ad8c1c4356a29513afa2","tid":1325032,"uid":161436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:34:33.000Z","msg":"721見！！！！！"},{"pid":"733c1a1cd1749147363c01a186a190b1872c39b1","tid":1325032,"uid":34877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"給香港警察最後忠告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322045\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322045</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"406db25bd1e16075510f9eefd7d1e5e297277456","tid":1325032,"uid":274598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:36:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/357605441108571/posts/1037708629764912?s=1344445283&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F357605441108571%2Fposts%2F1037708629764912%3Fs%3D1344445283%26sfns%3Dmo&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=c0b3265b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/357605441108571/posts/1037708629764912?s=1344445283&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n【如果金鐘主要幹道被封　可以怎樣逃生】（請廣傳，如有更好方法也請提供）<br />\n<br />\n本周日金鐘將有大型集會，經過沙田新城巿廣場血戰，見識過防暴便衣濫打的殘暴。若果金鐘主要幹道被堵，參與抗爭的手足，一定要熟路知道有甚麼活門可以逃離。<br />\n<br />\n惟一逃生的活門是太古廣場，若果太古頂不住壓力提早拉閘，連入都不能入，而圖中的主要幹道都被封鎖，基本上是無路可逃的，除了衝上海富寫字樓，例如李柱銘律師行（可能要通知Martin周日晚要營業）等會收留的地方，我也想不到甚麼方法。<br />\n<br />\n但如果太古廣場照常營業，即使警方同時殺到，還是有路可走：<br />\n1. 上鄰近金鐘政府合署的自動電梯，一直上到頂然後轉左入香格里拉酒店及毗鄰的港麗酒店暫避；轉右就是香港公園，一直往中環方向走，如果中環安全就可以中環坐船離開。（參考二樓附圖）<br />\n<br />\n2. 太古廣場三樓，逆金鐘廊方向一直走，名店Loewe及Celine中間，溥儀眼鏡後面，有四部電梯上港麗酒店，坐到L層就是酒店大堂，可暫避。（參考三樓附圖）<br />\n<br />\n3. 太古廣場三樓，逆金鐘廊方向一直走，到盡頭有通往萬豪酒店的門，可去酒店暫避。（參考三樓附圖）<br />\n<br />\n4. 太古廣場LG1，有一條通道往地鐵站，中間有分叉路去皇后大道東、日月星街的太古廣場三期。到太古三期後出灣仔散水。（參考LG1附圖）<br />\n<br />\n5. 如果中環、灣仔都查，而酒店無法留，最後一著就是沿正義道，經英國領事館（右）及亞洲協會（左），一直到盡頭，上樓梯至堅尼地道。再由堅尼地道往灣仔、銅鑼灣逃。（參考附圖Google Map）<br />\n<br />\n還有兩部自動電梯在三樓，通往太古廣場一、二期的寫字樓大堂，但不建議去，因為空空如也的大堂，保安可能趕人，不宜留。<br />\n<br />\n如果連中環、灣仔、銅鑼灣都大規模搜捕，最後一個方法是由堅尼地道上寶雲徑走山路逃生。<br />\n<br />\n如果不熟識太古廣場的朋友有時間，絕對值得這兩天來先踩踩線，摸清楚商場各個出入位。"},{"pid":"dac259d8c14f3659699448e76a1772c4ce8949b6","tid":1325032,"uid":137237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:37:04.000Z","msg":"717遮打 721金鐘"},{"pid":"db182bdd733f239970132a1826c0a1ac51599605","tid":1325032,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:40:55.000Z","msg":"721一齊去港島"},{"pid":"cad2658db8a9d4a033d826ae7b0ad70ab3977d43","tid":1325032,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:41:23.000Z","msg":"我愛樓主"},{"pid":"438f708a9d0dee7bfc8d0864762536c172ab3488","tid":1325032,"uid":280595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:42:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8ac805f5d74ff1041d785d7ec2a72cb7ea7eea7","tid":1325032,"uid":191392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:44:08.000Z","msg":"唔理衝唔衝 721金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11071debb8654ba1e38005d4e483900229cba246","tid":1325032,"uid":272621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:44:13.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c618e921f10a1ceb7bd258408f362215758d63f6","tid":1325032,"uid":272621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:44:24.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe51ee2051ee57c2091c6e9c88da8a3f3423451","tid":1325032,"uid":272621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T18:45:07.000Z","msg":"721<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi